enhanced_by.reason: The sourceAssetList method provides necessary source asset details required for the one-time transaction.
The indexInfo method provides details about the index, which might be necessary for setting up the transaction parameters.
The oneTimeTransactionStatus method provides the status of the transaction, which can be used to verify the success or failure of the one-time transaction.
The planSubsHistory method provides historical transaction details, which can be used to verify the transaction history after the one-time transaction.
